---
title: Hot Honey and Ricotta Focaccia Serves 2 | with Arugula and Parmesan
description: This appy is the perfect combo sweet and salty with just the right amount of kick! Golden baked focaccia spread with creamy ricotta and Parmesan, then topped with peppery arugula and finished with a generous drizzle of addictive hot honey.
